Description: A square ivory label: perforated for attachment in the top right-hand corner. The front surface is inscribed in hieroglyphs.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: 'Macgregor Sale Catalogue (1922)', 676b; P. E. Newberry, ‘Proceedings of the Society of Biblical Archaeology’ 34 (London, 1912), 284 and pl. XXXI, 1; P.
